        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued August 2 at 10:47PM EDT by NWS Peachtree City GA</headline>
        <description>At 1047 PM EDT, a strong thunderstorm was near Forney. This storm was
nearly stationary.

HAZARD...Heavy rain.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Heavy rain may cause temporary street flooding especially
in poor drainage areas.

Locations impacted include...
Cave Spring and Etna.
</description>
        <instruction>Motorists should slow down and be prepared for possible loss of
control due to hydroplaning.</instruction>
